parameters: Shall we proceed with the operation?
Thief Nora: I think this area is good for an ambush...
Thief Nora: A-Are you really going to do it?
Mage Relm: I'll do it, my thoughts haven't changed!

Mage Relm: And it's not just my plan alone, it will
definitely work out because everyone is here!

Clea: We don't have any confirmation that the enemy is
coming, but let's proceed with the plan.

Priestess Sophia: If we try it for a little while and it
doesn't work, let's go back. We're running out of wine...
Mage Relm: Honestly... there's no sense of tension here.
Mage Relm: Alright, everyone except me, please hide!

Mage Relm (Just one step away from completing the
grimoire... hehehe, finally, my dream will come true!)

Mage Relm (Oops, I shouldn't have said that. We were in the
middle of a plan to lure out those troublemakers.)

Thief Nora (I hear footsteps from the back... I'm not sure
if it's the enemy, but we should be cautious!)

Mage Relm (Nora's signal... If I listen carefully, I can
indeed hear it too)
Mage Relm: Huh... why are you here?

Court Mage Eratoma: Ahaha, what a coincidence! Perhaps it's
fate that I've crossed paths with all of you.

Mage Relm: Didn't you give a warning? There's an incident
of mages going missing!

Mage Relm: It's dangerous to be alone in a place like
this!

Court Mage Eratoma: What is your dream? A part of a
dragon's corpse, moss as a medium for magic...

Court Mage Eratoma: I must say, I have a great interest in
magic users.

Mage Relm: I can't talk about my research because of the
circumstances at the Magic Academy.

Mage Relm: You shouldn't be able to talk about your
research either, as a court mage. There must be a lot of
confidential information.
Court Mage Eratoma: I am researching dragons.

Mage Relm: By the way, I heard that the royal palace has
also been secured. It seems there's no problem in discussing
the dragon dissection research.
Court Mage Eratoma: And, the creation of dragons.

Court Mage Eratoma: Did you not hear? I am researching the
method of creating dragons.

Court Mage Eratoma: The first time was a [unexpected
interruption], which was very, very sad, but the second time
yielded results!

Court Mage Eratoma: Well... it was in an uncontrollable
state, so I have to say it was a failure in terms of
results, you know.

Court Mage Eratoma: By the way, do you know why dragons can
fly!?

Court Mage Eratoma: Dragons fly because they are beautiful!
They are allowed to dance in the vast sky because they are
beautiful!
Mage Relm: What have you been--

Court Mage Eratoma: Ahaha, don't you understand? I am the
one who created the dragons that you defeated.

Court Mage Eratoma: Creating dragons requires a massive
amount of magical power. Taking the lessons from the
previous attempt, we should increase the amount of magical
power even more.

Court Mage Eratoma: There is a talented magician right in
front of me. Now, would you be willing to help me with my
dream?

Court Mage Eratoma: It was a very exciting experience. It's
not a bad idea to occasionally leave the laboratory, you
know.

Court Mage Eratoma: Well then, until another opportunity
arises.
Priestess Sophia: ...I won't let you escape.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
